summary: Malcolm Ethridge, managing partner at Capital Area Planning Group and author of Financial Independence Doesn't Happen by Accident, drops by to chat about the state of cybersecurity and why investors may be a little too pessimistic about Apple's future.  To catch full episodes of all The Motley Fool's free podcasts, check out our podcast center .  Should you invest $1,000 in Chipotle Mexican Grill right now?
